<br>
About Red Dwarf Bandits....<br>
<br>
There are some just out of Camelot's North Gate.   Run west towards the hills and you'll see a guard tower and a lone gaurd(jergenson or something).   Just east from the tower a bit is a campfire with dwarves around it.  If you kill off the brawlers, and other ones milling about, a Red Dwarf bandit will show up.<br>
<br>
Spot two.. Cross the double bridge.  On the north side, head east along the water and up into a thicket.  You'll find a shaman there and Red Bandit Dwarves.  If you open a dialog with the shaman and follow it thru to the end, she'll summon a couple pets and if you are along and level 20 or less, you're going to probably die.   The pets spawn on you and unless they are grey, you're not going to have much of a chance.<br>
<br>
There are also random dwarves that appear on the road from the bridge to the gaurd tower where the spiders are.   These are very infrequent pops, so not worth bothering with.<br>
<br>
-Mal<br>
